fixes k :: real
shows  "((1 / (2 * k))^(-2) * (-k)^3) = -4 * k powr 5"

theorem
fixes k :: real
shows  "((1 / (2 * k))^(-2) * (-k)^3) = -4 * k powr 5"
 proof- 
  show ?thesis sledgehammer
